title: Google\Cloud\Build\V1\Network
name: Network
description:
Network describes the GCP network used to create workers in.

Generated from protobuf message google.devtools.cloudbuild.v1.Network

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.project_id
params.description: Project id containing the defined network and subnetwork. For a peered VPC, this will be the same as the project_id in which the workers are created. For a shared VPC, this will be the project sharing the network with the project_id project in which workers will be created. For custom workers with no VPC, this will be the same as project_id.

params.name: data.network
params.description: Network on which the workers are created. "default" network is used if empty.

params.name: data.subnetwork
params.description: Subnetwork on which the workers are created. "default" subnetwork is used if empty.
